title: Not for everyone
review: I found this offbeat, weird and totally brilliant. This may not be for everyone but definitely a movie you wont forget. Highly recommended.

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode IX - The Rise of Skywalker
title: Disney at their best
review:
No originality, un-inspiring and underdeveloped characters, recycled plots and strategically placed porgs.
Eventually Disney ruin everything....Mission accomplished. Let the merchandising begin.

title: Fantastic Film
review: Another prime example of just how out of touch and irrelevant critics opinions are today. This is an awesome film and Rami is incredible.
